snippet.title: Introducing Galactic Getaway
snippet.description:
From the creators of Nookazon, we bring you Galactic Getaway!  Explore the galaxy, compete in thrilling minigames, customize your character, and create the ultimate vacation destination in this exciting multiplayer game!

Wishlist on Steam 💫 https://store.steampowered.com/app/2012390/Galactic_Getaway/
Join our Discord 💫 https://discord.gg/kTy7jyKdqG
